{"tid":338130,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[IOS/AN] 回合制PVP戰棋《榮耀戰棋》絕對考你戰術，部署既遊戲！","createTime":"2017-07-28T02:18:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-10T05:57:49.000Z","uid":130943,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e85117ea7ad3206edff45bc9aa890ffeabc12328","tid":338130,"uid":130943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T02:18:12.000Z","msg":"之前篇文可能主題誤導左大家，決定再開過新post, 如果admin 覺得重覆請幫忙del 舊post<br />\n<br />\n同大家介紹下一隻韓國game, 中文介面，開頭接觸以為簡簡單單，畫面唔係特別靚，但玩落原來變化極大！一玩真係上晒癮，同埋間公司都有心做隻GAME, 雖然出左2個月, 但都已經有過2次大既平衡修改, 可見官方好有心去搞好隻game. 真心要同大家推薦下<br />\n而家仲要大更新完好多活動同獎勵，一入game 已送一張夠升4級既英雄比大家等大家易啲起手！<br />\n<br />\n呢款係回合式戰棋，同時結合卡牌game 既玩法<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n首先講下玩法，呢隻遊戲入面有分英雄卡/士兵卡/法術卡，每張卡都有佢自己對應既cost。<br />\n<br />\n英雄有自己固定既兵種及有三個技能兼有裝備，會跟據英雄卡等級去開放（最高6級），去到四級時可以自己改變兵種及兵數，六級時，技能英雄可以自己替換<br />\n<br />\n兵種就有分 弓兵（遠程攻加乘）/長槍兵（每回合回血兼反擊加乘/騎馬兵（可以移動2格兼移動後攻擊有加乘）<br />\n<br />\n玩家首先要組合自己既deck（總數14張），英雄再加上士兵，就會成為部隊，可以啟動士兵特性。<br />\n<br />\n開戰時雙方響一個3*5既地圖到開戰，雙方一開始每人有5資源去出兵，唔同既卡消耗唔同資源，之後就靠大家響戰場上既部署去征服對手！<br />\n<br />\n勝利條件有三樣，一係全滅敵人，一係鬥快搶到人地主城，又或者勝利點數先到達30，是旦達到其中一項就贏<br />\n<br />\n遊戲本身貨幣分靈魂石及金幣，靈魂石就係比大家去換金幣或直接開寶箱抽英雄，如果大家唔想抽籤，可以直接用金幣去神殿開自己想要既英雄，不過每12個鐘至會更新一次，每次3隻，刷到有自己想要既英雄就要少少時間。為英雄升級亦都係靠響神殿買英雄靈魂再去訓練所升。<br />\n<br />\n另外遊戲設有公會，可以比大家用捐資源為專屬既特強公會英雄升級。<br />\n另外除左正常既排名戰，亦有競技場模式，無視自己現有既deck, random 去抽選6張牌比大家好公平咁，憑自己既技術去贏！<br />\n<br />\n比少少tips 大家，升英雄時揀佢既技能系統同埋裝備，因為呢隻game 真正既樂趣係當大家都擁有六級英雄時，可以自訂技能，到時鬥既就係成隊人入面，大家技能組合既強弱！<br />\n<br />\n暫時講住咁多，但大家裝完玩過再慢慢一齊研究！<br />\n提提大家，開頭可以玩下單人模式熟習左個遊戲系統先，同完成時可以拎齊啲法術卡<br />\n<br />\nDownload 連結響到，大家經我既𨘋請好友連結去安裝遊戲會額外有多500靈魂石<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://ua.withhive.com/ua556454c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fua.withhive.com%2Fua556454c&d=bike7XMNu5WEBsN6JscLttU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=bd07cd57\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">ua.withhive.com/ua556454c</a> <br />\n<br />\n有咩唔明可以響到留言再問，識既盡量解答<br />\n<br />\n本人id #4C5DLJ , 歡迎加好友<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/28/101421_149d28219564624bc3fc0d4b603d20a8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F28%2F101421_149d28219564624bc3fc0d4b603d20a8.jpg&h=7de652f0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/28/101450_99437cf2e7d02615cd21662fcf50039a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F28%2F101450_99437cf2e7d02615cd21662fcf50039a.jpg&h=62238525&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/28/101504_ceb379082011f10157444edb1f0b5f25.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F28%2F101504_ceb379082011f10157444edb1f0b5f25.jpg&h=fe755f19&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/28/101516_1a8bf060f191ad97ec4d1676a37f32a7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F28%2F101516_1a8bf060f191ad97ec4d1676a37f32a7.jpg&h=5c26a75a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dd9066a7df834d97a7baeb41ff8e5b9f978e83d2","tid":338130,"uid":28163,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T04:54:05.000Z","msg":"幾好玩 幫推<br />\nCom2us出品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5306b98bdcec6383aaecb404771c5a886ab0d9ea","tid":338130,"uid":130943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T05:06:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾好玩 幫推<br />\nCom2us出品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n終於有知音人，呢隻我玩左近2個月都仲覺得好好玩，始終都係對人pvp 既game 入坑度大啲，要啲技術同要用下腦玩"},{"pid":"16b53f61d968a2af922d2ac64e3575dff8f1114a","tid":338130,"uid":130943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T04:39:55.000Z","msg":"頂一頂先"},{"pid":"6b96a7b52d09ebd5ca58012223443933a8818ccc","tid":338130,"uid":19643,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T13:33:44.000Z","msg":"幾好玩"},{"pid":"20600bf2fa97305915ef39b2879141bcc6aaa665","tid":338130,"uid":130943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T14:19:01.000Z","msg":"早2日削完快攻後好玩左，以前快攻橫行會嚇走新玩家，而家真係可以認真諗下點行"},{"pid":"089b8339e58eccc77d76421719db8c2e1c6aa798","tid":338130,"uid":130943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T04:52:46.000Z","msg":"自頂多一下"},{"pid":"8050d0645609b361c7296db4816216d5ca71339a","tid":338130,"uid":130943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T11:12:25.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"83a57b7556be2c90592e08276c6e8fa6cb1c1367","tid":338130,"uid":77715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T15:14:36.000Z","msg":"本身鐘意玩戰棋game, 岩岩dl左落黎試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76aec4ca5013e83b3921960da454aa3155e448d8","tid":338130,"uid":130943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T00:44:58.000Z","msg":"鐘意玩戰棋又鐘意對人戰既真係要試下，我打到上3700分真係戇膠膠行錯一步或者一心急就贏緊都輸返落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n提下有心玩既，真係咪貪果一個半個資源或者據點，行前一步人地隨時三對弓兵招呼你"},{"pid":"05603c1d738a93acc876174d583322f4cfe6b347","tid":338130,"uid":100736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T00:54:03.000Z","msg":"lm返屋企記得既話就試"},{"pid":"bc40668301b2f5a450cf2275539f68612ba7d8f7","tid":338130,"uid":130943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T08:45:54.000Z","msg":"新玩記得玩下單人學左啲基本操作先，同埋競技場而家24小時開放，隨機比你揀7張牌，全英雄都最高級，可以比你地有排練英雄升級都可以享受下隻game"},{"pid":"b283825fd516e02d9dc2201757df61b683a8b74c","tid":338130,"uid":130943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T07:31:44.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"4d629dec8e8a8375f779b0b05f5a7001439a188e","tid":338130,"uid":130943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T06:52:13.000Z","msg":"近期係咁送錢送石，新手入坑係時候啦"},{"pid":"18cb0eb1178838f8b78dcebe01160ce3f3a47088","tid":338130,"uid":33721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T08:46:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>近期係咁送錢送石，新手入坑係時候啦</blockquote><br />\n係咪要刷首抽"},{"pid":"20ac873f159202dcb9626f184bf850ec0f4e99a3","tid":338130,"uid":33721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T09:16:10.000Z","msg":"完全唔知要做咩"},{"pid":"b04bab7444b093038a78df7dfaa78f04003eb371","tid":338130,"uid":130943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T14:38:20.000Z","msg":"唔駛刷首抽，反正佢神殿會不停更新，見岩用既人就買再升"},{"pid":"83cb78d9f10b2a889128d931165ac694ad157676","tid":338130,"uid":130943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T14:39:57.000Z","msg":"起手㨂幾隻有用既英雄升上4級，已經夠打上2000-3000分，玩熟左至再慢慢研究邊啲英雄既配搭有用"},{"pid":"010c0331fb9165116922df2d33cd23e1895475c7","tid":338130,"uid":130943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T14:42:27.000Z","msg":"起手易用既英雄可以用 雅典娜 李舜臣 厄洛斯 樹長老 矮人 同有隻回血既槍兵女神<br />\n<br />\n呢隻game 主要係回血技能/加防技能/術防技能/加自身攻擊力既技能係最有用<br />\n玩耐左再慢慢睇下啲對手技能配搭，邊啲自己覺得勁既就參考下，大致上係咁玩"},{"pid":"c09ededf9fb177f1b2be50938161590d02b0d58b","tid":338130,"uid":130943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T14:47:20.000Z","msg":"呢隻game 變化其實好大，不過都要係玩到中後期起左自己套deck 至感受到，當組左自己隊時，就係慢慢研究配技轉兵種，因為英雄去到4級時可以轉兵種兵力，去到6級時可以自換技能<br />\n<br />\n所以去到3600分以上，起手咩角色其實已經唔重要，因為啲人既技大多都轉晒，大家鬥係技能配搭，點樣砌一套卡去秒人或者磨死人地<br />\n<br />\n希望多啲朋友一齊加入研究下"},{"pid":"ab7fbc9da23554317c5e0fd1107b3fce94829da3","tid":338130,"uid":130943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T09:24:57.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"da0eea8a32612ed6b6a7213caf3f2ae49cc1fa8d","tid":338130,"uid":130943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T04:02:48.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c9d1c7b103208755877a204f318c46e5371663bf","tid":338130,"uid":100736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T14:51:48.000Z","msg":"down左 幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b8e8aefb6589c4f5f59383122a49536b7bbe089","tid":338130,"uid":130943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T16:59:34.000Z","msg":"初中段可能會覺得變化無咁大，因為都係依賴某特定英雄，但升到之後好多野研究<br />\n<br />\n如果起手想易玩，用術隊，有格林同世宗大王2個既畫龍點睛技能可以buff 術攻，夠炸到人飛起"},{"pid":"fc3d8570b90b8677c91a84423ff4d926ec3b07a1","tid":338130,"uid":46538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T10:21:19.000Z","msg":"新手第一日玩，岩岩見神殿出左隻4lv 9尾，3萬幾金。用唔用石換金買好？"},{"pid":"3a570345ebd76de414b3396bcac09f5354dbb69f","tid":338130,"uid":130943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T18:09:02.000Z","msg":"九尾啲技都ok ，後段都仲會有用，可以買左佢黎用住先<br />\n<br />\n到升左5級搏佢綠色技出回血. 不過去到6級都會自己換技，到時可以紫色換貫通，綠色用自己回血<br />\n<br />\n不過換技要用100本書，都起碼係比較中段後既事"},{"pid":"258830aeaf3207c29d3905ca2ae4aa535a9be3ff","tid":338130,"uid":46538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T03:05:03.000Z","msg":"今日神殿有4級阿瑞斯&hellip; 但依家得1萬，點樣可以快d 賺到金幣？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7506cf049751d522d589ab35894f0a59576cbbee","tid":338130,"uid":130943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T03:37:44.000Z","msg":"金幣真係無得急，一係就用石換錢，一係就等平時打贏果啲啲錢同三勝箱，另外分解啲裝備同捐野比公會都可以有錢。不過呢幾日活動都送錢<br />\n<br />\n啲石最好全部留黎換錢，初段中段最缺錢，抽其他野好伏"},{"pid":"88f2996a14a19e039996df827a61d55c49834ce4","tid":338130,"uid":130943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T03:38:43.000Z","msg":"不過阿瑞斯麻麻，起手唔係算好用<br />\n<br />\n同埋如果無錢既，買啲一級二級既英雄慢慢升啦，因為每升一次英雄又拎到技能書"},{"pid":"fa4da1887c4d3e716c8d820deca611f4f1637f30","tid":338130,"uid":46538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T04:17:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不過阿瑞斯麻麻，起手唔係算好用<br />\n<br />\n同埋如果無錢既，買啲一級二級既英雄慢慢升啦，因為每升一次英雄又拎到技能書</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有咩英雄推介，同埋d石用係邊到最好？"},{"pid":"605822c7c501aa0c5c2f5e4afa1b1a3bf6b1864c","tid":338130,"uid":130943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T05:09:31.000Z","msg":"如果未諗到升到6級咁長遠，就揀起手技能有用既<br />\n<br />\n坦角色推介樹長老，矮人，回血盾就瓦爾基里，玩術攻就格林同世宗大王，術防就李舜臣 雅典娜，輸出攻手就武藏 拿破崙<br />\n<br />\n玩到後期規劃，就睇技既顏色配搭。紫紅技能就係輸出向，綠藍 就回復盾，大致係咁<br />\n<br />\n啲石建議用黎換錢，最實用"},{"pid":"14bed60c219085532ac4af72af297ba2e241a947","tid":338130,"uid":46538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T04:40:21.000Z","msg":"單人22關過唔到，有冇教學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af635f374897aa25156e1fa9b86d6410c03deca6","tid":338130,"uid":130943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T07:49:57.000Z","msg":"九尾移下一格，上兵，主營就放一隻槍兵，再用築建大本營。 引左電腦過黎同利用大本營有buff 引佢地出術硬食一下先，之後下回合就用九尾射行左過黎既槍兵，自己本營果隻再上埋英雄但唔好行，保持2隻一齊，要不停回血。同埋就要用回歸整走一隻，再加障壁擋一擋，你務求要自己挨到呢個回合，如果挨到既話都基本上贏硬"},{"pid":"bd9d567e6d115781e113ad57909f2ab78297dce3","tid":338130,"uid":130943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T04:40:05.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"0e86e4e609b4c3a5db8b9fda694cd2edeea89542","tid":338130,"uid":130943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T18:09:32.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"0e96b932a43aec5cf599a7d9d8d9b8a7b43bbd8e","tid":338130,"uid":65653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T13:36:57.000Z","msg":"新手覺得有d難玩"},{"pid":"6bc89630669ce165ca32e0f4b05a3fd3034e2789","tid":338130,"uid":130943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T00:40:22.000Z","msg":"你可以玩單人模式頭幾關熟左個系統先，主要玩法其實都唔難上手，不過打上高分真係要再研究至得"},{"pid":"d9783696373edf8f205ce2636ad454fad2e9889b","tid":338130,"uid":65653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T05:12:32.000Z","msg":"第11點打"},{"pid":"d658d880c068639253abcb10fb557af812df2c7f","tid":338130,"uid":62646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T11:59:46.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e3a02a0d2c8ab1e77b979b652e3f413f4a3bc272","tid":338130,"uid":9707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T17:29:57.000Z","msg":"聽日dl黎玩下先"},{"pid":"4e78e8e236423c85057fb651ae24020e283425d5","tid":338130,"uid":9707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T18:55:08.000Z","msg":"好似冇咩人玩咁"},{"pid":"ec86a6ea6d3565ff48a76f0514a84ea273b438da","tid":338130,"uid":130943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T10:08:37.000Z","msg":"香港係少人玩，可能太花時間去研究，我地其他香港玩家都有個whatsapp gp, 有興趣可入"},{"pid":"34781fb3ed90d35c59dac4d08404d864c3425881","tid":338130,"uid":9707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T14:48:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港係少人玩，可能太花時間去研究，我地其他香港玩家都有個whatsapp gp, 有興趣可入</blockquote><br />\n巴打係唔係係game叫入入gp果位？"},{"pid":"06774f44ec3ced99c4b5386b45c1c30c0a40c5ae","tid":338130,"uid":130943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T01:03:13.000Z","msg":"果個唔係我。不過都係同一個whatsapp gp, 如果你仲有玩可以入去一齊研究下，啲牌組要集思廣益至掂😂 一升錯人就浪費好多資源"},{"pid":"f67eb73d369e82951b04b640f4a510beff4f5dc2","tid":338130,"uid":9707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T18:28:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>果個唔係我。不過都係同一個whatsapp gp, 如果你仲有玩可以入去一齊研究下，啲牌組要集思廣益至掂😂 一升錯人就浪費好多資源</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我一條友單機緊咋"},{"pid":"63474e4a86c1e5156400a07629645c4f4c9873c5","tid":338130,"uid":130943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T00:30:03.000Z","msg":"單機好悶架 對人排名戰試下自己個deck 至過癮"},{"pid":"98e18fdd4789e1b54cbef9b78a9a561171811f8b","tid":338130,"uid":9707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T08:04:59.000Z","msg":"我都有同其他玩家玩過既，不過唔知自己副deck如何<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/29/160433_a047b899717e0860ed3472adb4037129.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F29%2F160433_a047b899717e0860ed3472adb4037129.jpg&h=67604557&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"82fc1954b90b0ff704d990a679fa4f0b9a4dacbe","tid":